               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Risālah fī kalimat al-tawḥīd by Nūr Allāh Aʿẓamʹpūrī‏</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1071-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>A Persian paraphrase and extensive commentary on an Arabic treatise on divine unity by 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8010" role="aut">Muḥammad Nūr Allah ibn Muḥammad Muqīm al-Dīn Aʻz̤ampūrī</persName>who completed an earlier work in 1244 (1828/29). The author of the Arabic work being commented on is repeatedly referred to as Mawlānā ʻAbd al-Raḥmān which can therefore be identified as the 
                <title key="work_22916">Risālah fī kalimat al-tawḥīd</title>by 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_90042997" role="aut">Jāmī</persName>. The Arabic text, overlined in red, begins on f. 10v. For a Persian version of this work see Or.8018, ff.1-5. 14 lines per page; cursive nastaʻliq; rubrications; slightly worm-eaten; 19th century.
                        </p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656327.0x000001 viaf_118072896">Nūr Allāh Aʿẓamʹpūrī‏</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_118072896">‏نورالله اعظمپوری</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22916">​al-Nūr al-muṭlaq fī tarjumat kalimat al-ḥaqq</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_22916">​النور المطلق فی ترجمة کلمة الحق</title>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
